author: baranda
msg: Removed functionality from ResponseWriterImpl.endCode() that provoked MYFACES-152 and MYFACES-883. Now it is possible to use the f:view tag before the body tag. The myfaces javascript code is created in the viewTag.doEndTag() method but it is not inserted in the response till the ExtensionsFilter does the post-parsing.
